                  <decoDesc>
                     <summary>The illustrations on this bifolio are executed in the <term key="PostGondarineStyle"/>.  The figures have been at first outlined with black ink, and then partly filled in with red, blue, yellow and black.</summary>
    
                     <decoNote type="miniature" xml:id="d1">
                        <locus target="#1v"/>
                         <desc>A representation of the <ref type="authFile" corresp="AT1031VirginAndChild"/>.
                             <persName ref="PRS6819Mary"/> with the infant <persName ref="PRS5684JesusCh"/> is surrounded by two <term key="angel">angels</term>.</desc>
                     </decoNote>
                      
                      <decoNote type="miniature" xml:id="d2">
                          <locus target="#1v"/>
                          <desc> An <ref type="authFile" corresp="AT1012Equestrian"/> portrait of
                              <persName ref="PRS4585Georgeo"/> killing the <term key="dragon"/>.</desc>
                      </decoNote>
                      
                      <decoNote type="miniature" xml:id="d3">
                          <locus target="#1v"/>
                          <desc>A representation of the <ref type="authFile" corresp="AT1036MercyCovenant"/>. 
                              <persName ref="PRS6819Mary"/>, to the left, has <term key="gesturecrossed">crossed arms</term>. 
                              <persName ref="PRS5684JesusCh"/>, to the right, performs a <term key="gestureblessing"/>.
                              </desc>
                      </decoNote>
    
                     <decoNote type="miniature" xml:id="d4">
                        <locus target="#2r"/>
                         <desc>A depiction of the <ref type="authFile" corresp="AT1030Trinity"/>. 
                             Each figure performs a <term key="gestureblessing"/> with his right and holds a <term key="globe"/> in his left.
                             Their octagonal <term key="mandorla"/> is surrounded by the <term key="tetramorph"/> arranged in the 
                             <term>Angel⇨Eagle⇨Ox⇨Lion</term> order.</desc>
                     </decoNote>

                     <decoNote type="miniature" xml:id="d5">
                        <locus target="#2r"/>
                        <desc> A representation of the <ref type="authFile" corresp="AT1005Crucifixion"/> of
                           <persName ref="PRS5684JesusCh"/>, who is shown as 
                            <term key="deadjesus">dead</term>
                            on the <term key="cross">cross</term> and has a <term key="halo">cruciform halo</term>.
                            The <term key="sunandmoon"/> are shown above the cross, while two weeping women are placed below it.</desc>
                     </decoNote>
    
                     <decoNote type="miniature" xml:id="d6">
                        <locus target="#2r"/>
                         <desc>The bottom right corner features a dabtara with an <term key="angel">angel</term>above him, this may be a 
                            <term key="donordepiction">donor portrait</term>.</desc>
                     </decoNote>
                  </decoDesc>


